{"tid":703021,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話說頭先去櫃員機拎錢","createTime":"2018-06-15T11:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T12:06:51.000Z","uid":162644,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4701cb5877a184117bf2e8039579f23ff8be3d68","tid":703021,"uid":162644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"係我前面個呀姐提款卡都無拎番就走左出去<br />\n到我追出去既時候已經搵唔到佢<br />\n因為我排隊掛住玩電話無留意佢衣著，出面又勁多人<br />\n依家我拎住張卡係手點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都企係到等左十分鐘都無人番黎搵張卡<br />\n但因為我約左女女食飯所以唔等就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定晏d拎去警署🤔"},{"pid":"6e79b66da0010fd87e67d96f3d8064d57b40ff9e","tid":703021,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39c26a246485499a20804cb7b30cf1a727a2b1db","tid":703021,"uid":63843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:36:21.000Z","msg":"保管住張卡 之後比返銀行 警署"},{"pid":"4714bf971a581ace5831f4a181fcf8aa0c76356a","tid":703021,"uid":3465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:36:47.000Z","msg":"差館 唔洗諗 你遲交出嚟有機會比人告偷野"},{"pid":"aebd60e29e44a318179caac153315818c7e5e6c9","tid":703021,"uid":2127,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:36:47.000Z","msg":"其實你唔拎返張卡 會自動收返入部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1ccd5757a7df232e7f5dff88b2407ead062fd5","tid":703021,"uid":162644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e79b66da0010fd87e67d96f3d8064d57b40ff9e","tid":703021,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:36:54.000Z","msg":"係呀斷到正，係咪要終身監禁"},{"pid":"22465a773f65175b1748da27b733c9fcfa99a70e","tid":703021,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/